    <mxCell id="p2-2112" parent="p2-1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#a07a4a;fillColor=#fdf5e8;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=8;fontColor=#3a1a00;strokeWidth=2;" value="&lt;b&gt;PLANK COUNT SUMMARY (planning est.)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Field planks: 48 &#215; 16-ft Trex 5.5&quot; (cut to 15&apos;-7&quot;, ~5&quot; waste ea.)&lt;br/&gt;PF house-side: 23&apos;-6&quot; (order 24-ft or splice from 16-ft)&lt;br/&gt;PF far-side: 23&apos;-6&quot; (same)&lt;br/&gt;PF left-side: 16&apos;-6&quot; (16-ft board, field-cut)&lt;br/&gt;PF right-side: 16&apos;-6&quot; (16-ft board, field-cut)&lt;br/&gt;Board subtotal: 52&lt;br/&gt;+10% waste: ~5 boards&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;TOTAL ORDER: ~57 boards (planning est.)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Hollis will produce precise BOM with cut list." vertex="1">
      <mxGeometry x="1210" y="180" width="420" height="240" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="p2-2113" parent="p2-1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#444444;fillColor=white;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=7;fontColor=#222222;" value="&lt;b&gt;LEGEND — PAGE 2: DECKING&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Field plank (tan #c9a778):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;5.5&quot; Trex Transcend, 48 planks @ 5.625&quot; c-c (5.5&quot; + 1/8&quot; gap), &#x22A5; house&lt;br/&gt;16-ft boards cut to 15&apos;-7&quot;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;PF board (dark tan #a07a4a):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;5.5&quot; Trex, all 4 sides. House + far = 23&apos;-6&quot; | L + R = 16&apos;-6&quot;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;CORNER JOINTS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Top corners (against house): BUTTED — not mitered&lt;br/&gt;Bottom corners (exposed): 45&#176; MITER&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;FRAMING (background @ 40% opacity):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Unchanged from Page 1. All tops at 11&quot; AG. Deck top at 12&quot; AG.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;ORDERING NOTES:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;48 &#215; 16-ft field boards + 4 PF boards = 52 + 10% = ~57 total&lt;br/&gt;PF long sides: prefer 24-ft; else splice from 16-ft over joist&lt;br/&gt;Trex Transcend 5.5&quot; Grooved or Solid Edge (match species/color)&lt;br/&gt;Hidden fasteners: Trex Hideaway for field; face-screw PF w/ Trex screws&lt;br/&gt;Carbide blade; cut from back face; 1/8&quot; spacers during install" vertex="1">
      <mxGeometry x="1210" y="435" width="420" height="420" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
